data.description: Embrace the perfect blend of countryside charm beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bath home, nestled on a sprawling 1.49-acre cul-de-sac lot. Just a stone's throw from vibrant downtown Angier and minutes from Highway 40, this property is ideally positioned for both tranquility and convenience. Laminate wood floors pave the way through a layout designed for easy living and entertaining, with granite countertops and updated cabinetry adorning the heart of the home.  Welcome guests from a picturesque rocking chair front porch and an expansive backyard that is a blank canvas, ready to be transformed into your dream outdoor sanctuary. Offering a rare combination of space, privacy, and accessibility, this Angier home is a unique find. Don't miss your chance to make this your own.
